  "aboutParagraph": `<p>
          Hi, my name is Gautam Jain. I am a Tech and Space Enthusiast. I am a
          CSE Major, and currently, I am working as a PA in Cognizant.
          <br />
          <br />
          I have been fascinated by the wondrous aspects of technology ever
          since I was a kid, and after getting my personal computer after 12th grade
          standard, my interest skyrocketed.
          <br />
          <br />I was so amazed by the cool operations one can perform using
          such small machines as a laptop and a phone. I begin to dive deep
          into the concepts of computer science, and to get more proficient
          in the field, enrolled for a
          <b style={{ textTransform: 'none' }}> Computer Science Undergraduate</b> degree.
          <br />
          <br />
        </p>
        <p
          className={showCollapsed ? '' : 'collapsible'}
          style={{ textTransform: 'none' }}
        >
          I graduated with my bachelor's degree from <b> GNDEC, Ludhiana</b> in
          August 2023. Throughout my course of 4 years, I invested in developing
          a good understanding of core computer science concepts like
          <b style={{ textTransform: 'none' }}>
            Discrete Mathematics, Data Structures and Algorithms, Operating Systems
            systems, Database management, CAM, Cyber Security, Compiler Design
          </b>{' '}
          etc.
          <br />
          <br />
          Along with my academics, I also invested in developing my problem-solving
          solving skills by actively indulging in competitive tournaments on
          platforms like
          <b style={{ textTransform: 'none' }}>
            GeeksforGeeks, Leetcode, Code Studio, Hacker Rank, Code chef and
            also made a routine of solving daily problems and challenges
          </b>{' '}
          .<br />
          <br />I worked together with my team (college friends and work
          colleagues) to create innovative, scalable, and open-source projects
          and gained experience in software development by working as a student
          <b style={{ textTransform: 'none' }}>
            SDE intern at E-Cell, TNP Cell, and 11 mantras
          </b>
          .<br />
          <br />I am currently working as a{' '}
          <b style={{ textTransform: 'none' }}>
            Programmer Analyst trainee at Cognizant Technology Solutions
          </b>
          , brushing up on my skills in technologies like
          <b>
            Oracle Apps, Oracle SQL, Oracle PL/SQL, Java, JSP, JDBC, Spring
          </b>{' '}
          etc.
          <br />
          <br />
          I am always open to opportunities to further polish my skills and get
          an insight into how the daily world functions with the help of
          technology.
          <br />
          <b style={{ textTransform: 'none' }}>
            Actively looking for open technology and project idea discussions.
          </b>
          <br />
          <br />
        </p>
